Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.20,0:00:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.54,0:00:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭 麥波
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.63,0:00:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.10,0:00:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為都已經第七碗了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.68,0:00:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都要更新記錄了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.01,0:00:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 我的咱們的蓋飯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.83,0:00:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.95,0:00:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.68,0:00:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跑去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.87,0:00:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別躲躲藏藏快出來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.49,0:00:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有一堆話想對你說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.84,0:00:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪…裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.78,0:00:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.60,0:00:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 蘭 麥波
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.96,0:00:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧？
